videos.description: Early in Game 1, Suns fans count out the number of seconds it takes Giannis Antetokounmpo to shoot a free throw.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Suns fans troll Giannis at the line) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Suns fans troll Giannis at the line

videos.description: Chris Paul finds Mikal Bridges on the fast break with a nice dime for a two-handed dunk to give the Suns the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 sets up Bridges for transition slam) 2021/06/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 sets up Bridges for transition slam

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo powers through Deandre Ayton as he throws down a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis muscles in for two-handed jam) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis muscles in for two-handed jam

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo comes flying down the court to swat away Mikal Bridges's layup, reminiscent of LeBron James on Andre Iguodala in 2016.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis flies in for LeBron-like block) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis flies in for LeBron-like block

videos.description: Dario Saric exits Game 1 with a right knee injury and is ruled out for the remainder of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Saric exits Game 1 with right knee injury) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Saric exits Game 1 with right knee injury

videos.description: Mikal Bridges' layup is off the mark, but Deandre Ayton grabs the board and throws down a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Ayton cleans up Bridges' miss with dunk) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ayton cleans up Bridges' miss with dunk

videos.description: Chris Paul takes a step to the side and pulls up to knock down a 3-pointer on Bobby Portis to push the Suns' lead to 86-68.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 gets a Breen 'Bang' on his 3 on Portis) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 gets a Breen 'Bang' on his 3 on Portis

videos.description: Cam Johnson pulls up to sink a transition jumper to give the Suns a 108-96 lead and ignites the Suns crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Cam Johnson sends Suns crowd into a frenzy) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cam Johnson sends Suns crowd into a frenzy

videos.description: Chris Paul drives straight to the bucket for a tough layup plus the foul late in Game 1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (CP3 drives in for dagger and-1) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 drives in for dagger and-1

videos.description: Chris Paul joins Malika Andrews after the Suns' 118-105 win over the Bucks in Game 1 to reflect on his first ever NBA Finals game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (CP3 reflects on his first NBA Finals appearance) 2021/07/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: CP3 reflects on his first NBA Finals appearance

videos.description: Chris Paul and Devin Booker combine for 59 points to lead the Suns to a 118-105 win vs. the Bucks in Game 1 of the NBA Finals.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (CP3, Booker and the Suns take Game 1 of the NBA Finals) 2021/07/06 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: CP3, Booker and the Suns take Game 1 of the NBA Finals
